      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my reliable ride. It\u2019s been such a great car for me\u2014always dependable and still running like a champ! It\u2019s in solid shape and has been well-cared for, though it\u2019s definitely seen some fun adventures. If you're looking for a trustworthy vehicle that\u2019s ready for the road, this is the one. I\u2019d love for you to come by, check it out, and see how smoothly it drives!",
