    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The mechanical vitals are strong, with a recent comprehensive VANOS service and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural integrity under load. The naturally aspirated powerplant delivers exceptionally linear torque and a sharp 8,000 RPM redline, breathing through individual throttle bodies. Handling remains precise thanks to a limited-slip differential and refreshed suspension bushings. While the exterior shows honest signs of road use, the drivetrain and chassis dynamics remain tight, offering the pure analog feedback that defines the E46 platform.",
      "price": 34500.0,
