    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle that perfectly embodies the 'driver\u2019s car'\u2014well-maintained, reliable, and ready for the road. The exterior finish retains a high-gloss luster, having been frequently garaged; while you may find a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper from standard use, the body lines remain straight and free of significant dents. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean. The leather seating surfaces are supple with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster, and the dashboard is free of cracks or sun damage. All interior electronics, including the premium sound system, navigation, and heated seats, have been tested and are fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with no hesitations, backed by a comprehensive service history that includes recent fluid flushes and a new set of high-performance all-season tires. The suspension is tight, providing a comfortable yet responsive ride without any unusual noises. This is an honest, turn-key vehicle for someone who appreciates a car that has been cared for correctly.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
