    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that balances sophisticated performance with enduring reliability. This unit has been thoroughly vetted to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for mechanical integrity and aesthetic presentation. It represents a distinguished choice for the discerning driver seeking a premium pre-owned experience that prioritizes both long-term value and operational excellence.",
