      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This high-revving power plant utilizes individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver a linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed via a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. This specimen has been mechanically sorted with documented rear subframe reinforcement and a recent VANOS overhaul. The suspension features refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, maintaining the chassis's legendary 50/50 weight distribution and communicative steering rack. While the exterior shows minor road patina consistent with its age, the drivetrain and structural integrity are excellent, making this a turn-key performance machine for the discerning enthusiast.",
